{"attrs": {}, "content_sha256": "sha256:8cf5bc3099f54cee", "depth": 4, "id": "problem_07/block.1/editor_notes.1/list.12/list_item.33", "order": 0, "role": "narrate", "span": {"end": 16440, "start": 16415}, "text": "Is every symbol defined?", "type": "list_item"}
{"attrs": {}, "content_sha256": "sha256:b9bfccaf1d14d2cd", "depth": 4, "id": "problem_07/block.1/editor_notes.1/list.12/list_item.34", "order": 1, "role": "narrate", "span": {"end": 16573, "start": 16446}, "text": "Does the rubric use exact answer / tolerance for objective questions or a structural / judge rubric for proof-style questions?", "type": "list_item"}
{"attrs": {}, "content_sha256": "sha256:5310293b3c9f95b2", "depth": 4, "id": "problem_07/block.1/editor_notes.1/list.12/list_item.35", "order": 2, "role": "narrate", "span": {"end": 16682, "start": 16579}, "text": "Can the verifier grade deterministically, or at least be audited line by line from the written schema?", "type": "list_item"}
{"attrs": {}, "content_sha256": "sha256:e0f339421058f13a", "depth": 4, "id": "problem_07/block.1/editor_notes.1/list.12/list_item.36", "order": 3, "role": "narrate", "span": {"end": 16736, "start": 16688}, "text": "Does the problem require non-routine reasoning?", "type": "list_item"}
